
> LOOK

Provides a detailed view of the space around you, including a list of other items, characters, and creatures that are there with you.

> LOOK IN|ON|BEHIND|UNDER <thing>

Provides a list of the items contained in/on/behind/under <thing>.

> LOOK <thing>
> LOOK <thing> IN|ON|BEHIND|UNDER <container>

Provides a detailed view of a specific <thing> including what it is holding and wearing.

